WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.983
Good morning, family, or good evening or wherever you are.

00:00:03.983 --> 00:00:06.149
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:06.149 --> 00:00:13.027
We're going to pray, but I want to go over what the Lord showed us yesterday in prayer.

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:21.320
I haven't had an experience like that ever on a live.

00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:36.200
You know, I have dreams, I have visions, that the Lord shows me quite a few things, but never like that where when I'm praying, I feel like I'm leaving.

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:41.415
And last night, that's why I told Diana, "Pray for me.

00:00:41.415 --> 00:00:45.904
Lay your hand on me," because it brings me back into reality a little bit.

00:00:45.904 --> 00:00:47.560
It snaps.

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:50.960
When I go into the spirit like that, I'm able to see so far.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:54.413
There are sometimes when I'm going in, I can see the years.

00:00:54.413 --> 00:00:57.300
I can see so much detail.

00:00:57.300 --> 00:00:59.180
I can smell things.

00:00:59.650 --> 00:01:02.240
It's heavenly.

00:01:02.240 --> 00:01:10.320
But at the same time, when you're in the natural, it has a tendency to freak your flesh out a little bit is what I want to tell you.

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:20.400
I don't know how else to describe it than it makes your flesh—because the spirit is more real to me than the natural body.

00:01:21.270 --> 00:01:26.560
Our spirit realm is more real than the natural realm.

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:34.120
And people, if you learn to tap into it and get in with the Holy Spirit and walk with him, he'll show you the things to come.

00:01:35.050 --> 00:01:42.560
But I'm telling you, the other side is just as real and more real than this realm.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:51.582
And when you start to get over and look over and see what God is doing, it's beautiful and you go, "Wow.

00:01:51.582 --> 00:01:55.720
" You know, I long for the day Jesus Christ comes and gets us.

00:01:55.720 --> 00:01:58.813
But I'm going to go over because a lot of people go, "Brandon, you okay?

00:01:58.813 --> 00:02:01.040
What's that all about?

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:11.920
" Well, to try to explain the supernatural in some things is like trying to explain a hot sandy beach to an Eskimo.

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:12.816
You don't.

00:02:14.900 --> 00:02:19.680
It's real hard because the Eskimo has no idea what it's like to feel the tropics.

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:23.446
He's only used to igloos and cold weather.

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:29.617
So, where do I start?

00:02:32.480 --> 00:02:33.505
I saw 2027.

00:02:33.505 --> 00:02:47.311
I saw the storm, but I saw the prophet, Kim Clement, and he was interceding for America, but he was playing on the other side.

00:02:48.573 --> 00:02:53.640
It was glorious, but he looked so young.

00:02:55.396 --> 00:03:01.290
I told Donna through a text earlier his skin looked like he had Botox.

00:03:01.290 --> 00:03:02.489
His skin had no wrinkles.

00:03:02.489 --> 00:03:05.490
He looked so fresh and clean.

00:03:05.490 --> 00:03:12.227
His shirt was red and he looked so pressed and like a dry-cleaned shirt.

00:03:12.227 --> 00:03:13.663
Everything looked so perfect.

00:03:13.663 --> 00:03:18.640
His hair was perfect and long just like it always was when he was on the earth.

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:37.000
But he was playing a keyboard that was like a plastic keyboard like we have here like a Yamaha or whatever, like a nice keyboard, but he was playing that keyboard and he was interceding and praying for America.

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:58.416
But remember, do you all remember whenever I had the vision of Lynn Hammond's sister Lucy and Rachel Tefatiller and Jeannie Wilkerson and they were sitting on the quilt and all that and it was the glorious time that I saw that they were praying, interceding with brother Halverson?

00:04:02.617 --> 00:04:07.160
This was similar to that.

00:04:10.229 --> 00:04:23.555
But as he was praying, there was this huge cloud behind him with lightning that was going around him and he was prophesying, but I couldn't make out what he was saying.

00:04:25.504 --> 00:04:26.352
He was declaring and he was speaking over America.

00:04:33.920 --> 00:04:34.653
And as he was playing his keyboard, you could feel the glory.

00:04:34.653 --> 00:04:42.088
I was watching him, but he was not moved by what was around him.

00:04:42.088 --> 00:04:51.189
He was focused on the task at hand in his heavenly body.

00:04:52.220 --> 00:04:54.510
And I thought, "What in the world am I seeing?

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:00.896
" But I was looking and I saw 2027, 2028.

00:05:06.800 --> 00:05:07.160
And I asked Donna, I said, "Did your dad say anything about 2027?

00:05:17.584 --> 00:05:17.772
" and she sent me the video and I've been watching it since she sent it and the anointing on this clip is amazing as he's playing.

00:05:17.772 --> 00:05:26.902
But it wasn't about 2028, but I thought it was interesting as I was interceding and we were praying for our nation.

00:05:29.970 --> 00:05:33.960
The Lord showed us so much, but I want to get to what the Lord showed me today as I was driving around.

00:05:36.327 --> 00:05:40.196
I went out and I was getting—you know, I like to feed the deer in our neighborhood.

00:05:41.857 --> 00:05:44.618
The deer like to come and eat the corn.

00:05:44.618 --> 00:06:03.502
So I put corn out and things for them because I like to get them to come up close to the house because I like to watch them.

00:06:03.502 --> 00:06:10.910
And the Lord spoke to me and he started talking to me about the Supreme Court justices.

00:06:10.910 --> 00:06:18.945
And he said to me, "Brandon, I told you I was giving this nation a window of opportunity for a great wealth transfer.

00:06:20.250 --> 00:06:25.320
You pray into their decision concerning the tariffs and the finances of America.

00:06:45.017 --> 00:06:45.383
" And I said, "Lord, what happens if it doesn't come to pass?

00:07:04.526 --> 00:07:04.811
What am I looking at?

00:07:08.220 --> 00:07:12.304
" He was so stern with me.

00:07:13.509 --> 00:07:17.720
He said, "It will come to pass.

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:19.920
You speak into it.

00:07:19.920 --> 00:07:26.880
There are no ifs and buts about it in the spirit realm with me.

00:07:28.880 --> 00:07:29.120
You say to the mountain, 'Be removed.

00:07:29.120 --> 00:07:32.640
' We will as a nation have revival.

00:07:32.640 --> 00:07:43.674
We will as a nation have a wave of the finances for the outpouring of the glorious church to fund this gospel and get it promoted around the world.

00:07:43.674 --> 00:07:45.470
We will be victorious.

00:07:49.780 --> 00:07:50.240
" He said, "You speak to it.

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:00.086
There is no plan B.

00:08:20.351 --> 00:08:20.733
You speak to it.

00:08:20.733 --> 00:08:29.577
" He rebuked me for having a mealy mouth, you know, like, "Oh Lord, what happens if it doesn't happen?

00:08:38.400 --> 00:08:39.000
" He said, "You speak.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:40.820
" He corrected me.

00:08:44.720 --> 00:08:58.789
And he said, "America must—you must, Brandon—this must take place for the glorious outpouring for a window of opportunity.

00:09:04.710 --> 00:09:04.920
" And I'm not trying to yell.

00:09:15.380 --> 00:09:15.615
It's just when the anointing starts coming on me, you have to deal with it.

00:09:15.615 --> 00:09:16.973
Turn your volume down.

00:09:19.890 --> 00:09:21.969
I just get tired of all of it.

00:09:22.356 --> 00:09:24.520
This is what he said to me: "I saw the wave.

00:09:28.533 --> 00:09:28.827
I told you you would have a wave.

00:09:28.827 --> 00:09:32.240
It will be a short-lived wave and there will be gold on them.

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:44.100
" He said, "Fill your pockets, for a great storm is coming, but I will always provide for my beloved Brandon.

00:09:44.100 --> 00:09:50.269
" There is a storm coming, church, but it's not yet.

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:52.760
He said, "Pray for Donald Trump, Brandon.

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:55.763
I'm using him for this season.

00:10:09.956 --> 00:10:10.240
" And the enemy would want him removed.

00:10:10.240 --> 00:10:12.424
His life is in danger.

00:10:12.424 --> 00:10:15.029
You must pray for him.

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:23.040
The enemy doesn't want him to live long and finish strong, to finish his assignment on the earth.

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:28.035
And he's not done yet.

00:10:28.035 --> 00:10:41.154
And the Lord strictly told me today when I was out doing what I was doing, "Brandon, you need to intercede for him.

00:10:41.154 --> 00:10:42.440
It's the church's responsibility.

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:57.396
" And I saw a financial outpouring still concerning certain metals and cryptos, concerning certain foreign currencies.

00:10:57.396 --> 00:11:00.000
Like I said, I'm not a financial adviser.

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:07.131
I cannot come on here and tell the body of Christ what to do because I can miss it just like anybody else can.

00:11:07.131 --> 00:11:08.126
I'm human.

00:11:08.126 --> 00:11:17.160
And I want to tell you when you see in part and hear in part, we're all works in progress.

00:11:24.225 --> 00:11:28.600
I want to tell you that, but when it comes to this, you need to pray about it for your own family and what God is telling you to do.

00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:29.760
It's not my job.

00:11:29.760 --> 00:11:36.580
So I want you to intercede for these things because the Lord said to me, "This is part of the outpouring.

00:11:37.250 --> 00:11:41.360
The wealth transfer is part of the end-time harvest.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:42.940
Do you understand?

00:11:45.060 --> 00:11:45.600
And I'm giving you a window.

00:11:45.600 --> 00:11:52.030
" And he said, "Brandon, you're already one year into that window.

00:11:52.040 --> 00:11:59.104
" And he said, "What will you do with the time that I have given you?

00:11:59.104 --> 00:12:02.200
" for an hourglass was filled up a little bit more.

00:12:02.200 --> 00:12:03.640
"What will you do with the time?

00:12:03.640 --> 00:12:08.740
I've extended the time for the church for this window.

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:13.830
" And I saw the wave.

00:12:13.830 --> 00:12:14.980
I saw the finances.

00:12:17.560 --> 00:12:17.764
I saw the blessing.

00:12:17.764 --> 00:12:18.787
But it's all connected.

00:12:20.400 --> 00:12:22.080
And that's like what I was hearing today.

00:12:23.427 --> 00:12:27.435
The enemy would try to put a kink in the hose.

00:12:27.435 --> 00:12:28.657
No more delays.

00:12:28.657 --> 00:12:31.194
It's called a divine reversal.

00:12:31.194 --> 00:12:41.040
It's time for the supernatural divine reversal in your finances, a supernatural blessing on your household.

00:12:41.760 --> 00:12:47.060
You see, the enemy is fighting because he knows his time is short.

00:12:47.373 --> 00:12:51.104
Just like it talks about in Revelation, the enemy knows.

00:12:51.104 --> 00:12:54.744
He knows, he sees.

00:12:54.744 --> 00:13:00.257
We went over two videos ago that his time is short, but the finances are his wheelhouse.

00:13:00.257 --> 00:13:08.027
And that was when we went into the wars and all the things that he's trying to do.

00:13:27.384 --> 00:13:27.608
But the Lord said, "Brandon, I'm giving you a window.

00:13:33.765 --> 00:13:33.950
Do you understand?

00:13:33.950 --> 00:13:38.600
But you have to be a contender that fights for it.

00:13:44.166 --> 00:13:44.371
You have to pray.

00:13:54.865 --> 00:13:55.000
You have to not have this 'well, whatever will be, will be' attitude.

00:13:55.000 --> 00:14:00.187
" David didn't have a "whatever will be, will be" attitude with the Goliath that was standing in front of him.

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:03.840
You know, "Lord, if you deliver me, you deliver.

00:14:05.720 --> 00:14:06.016
If you don't, you don't.

00:14:07.491 --> 00:14:09.945
The giant's pretty big; I guess if he takes my head...

00:14:09.945 --> 00:14:11.120
" He didn't have that.

00:14:11.120 --> 00:14:13.295
What did he have?

00:14:32.754 --> 00:14:33.063
He had a bulldog faith.

00:14:33.063 --> 00:14:39.460
He said, "Who is this that tries to defy the armies of the living God?

00:14:48.147 --> 00:14:48.373
This uncircumcised Philistine?

00:14:48.373 --> 00:14:48.600
Who is this?

00:15:03.920 --> 00:15:04.148
" But David went after the giant and took his head.

00:15:04.148 --> 00:15:07.693
He didn't have a plan B; he was all in.

00:15:10.760 --> 00:15:12.674
And he went after that giant with those five stones.

00:15:12.674 --> 00:15:26.360
Those five, in case, maybe probably just to give him a little comfort thinking, "Well, if I miss him the first time, I've got four more times to hit him.

00:15:26.360 --> 00:15:28.406
" But either way, he's going down.

00:15:28.406 --> 00:15:32.809
But it was the first stone because he did it by faith.

00:15:37.400 --> 00:15:43.435
And I want you to understand, the Lord said to us, "I'm making you the head, not the tail.

00:15:51.040 --> 00:15:51.240
" And he spoke to us and said, "Speak to the seeds of your ancestors.

00:15:52.239 --> 00:15:56.515
The seeds that they sowed that lie dormant in the ground, that they never claimed, they never harvested.

00:15:56.515 --> 00:16:00.040
They never spiritually claimed them.

00:16:00.040 --> 00:16:01.593
They gave to people.

00:16:01.593 --> 00:16:03.560
They gave to ministries.

00:16:03.560 --> 00:16:08.248
You know, even a thousand years of generations, I don't know.

00:16:08.248 --> 00:16:14.900
Just believe God for a supernatural harvest, that through your generational bloodline you reap the harvest.

00:16:14.900 --> 00:16:17.183
" I'm believing God for big.

00:16:17.183 --> 00:16:22.178
There's family members who don't know that they have a covenant and God will provide for them.

00:16:22.178 --> 00:16:31.900
But every seed produces after its own kind, and I'm laying hold to it for the generational seeds, for the generational blessing.

00:16:31.900 --> 00:16:37.097
Regarding Abraham's generational blessing: "I'll bless your generation—a thousand generations or more.

00:16:37.097 --> 00:16:44.480
" Look at how the Lord said that he would even bless Abraham's lineage.

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:47.737
As much as the sands or the stars, the blessing was on him.

00:16:49.209 --> 00:16:57.160
And the Lord said he's no respecter of persons and what God will do for one, he'll do for another.

00:16:57.160 --> 00:17:03.040
I believe that I am Abraham's seed; I am part of that lineage.

00:17:03.040 --> 00:17:11.735
Don't you believe with all your heart that this is going to be the biggest end-time harvest of souls we've ever seen before?

00:17:11.735 --> 00:17:19.120
It's time to believe God and have stretch marks, is what I'm trying to tell y'all.

00:17:19.120 --> 00:17:28.595
It's time to have spiritual stretch marks, to believe him for the supernatural, to believe him for the exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:17:37.240 --> 00:17:39.000
And I know that if the tariff thing doesn't get passed by the Supreme Court in the next couple days, we will see this 1930s-style crash.

00:17:44.333 --> 00:17:44.520
I just believe it.

00:17:52.270 --> 00:17:56.380
I saw Donald Trump in that canoe trying his hardest to not let the economy go over the edge for the greatest—I've told you concerning that last October, not this last October, the one before.

00:17:56.380 --> 00:17:58.435
He said, "My people have prayed, Brandon.

00:18:01.520 --> 00:18:01.800
I'm giving you extended time.

00:18:07.428 --> 00:18:07.640
" And I saw the dam, the economy, and all of it was cracking.

00:18:08.600 --> 00:18:11.520
And the Lord said it will be worse than the 1930s on steroids.

00:18:11.520 --> 00:18:15.039
For this generation doesn't even know how to plant a garden.

00:18:15.039 --> 00:18:18.500
This generation doesn't even know how to hunt.

00:18:18.500 --> 00:18:20.680
This generation doesn't know how to fish.

00:18:32.204 --> 00:18:32.400
A lot of them are used to going to McDonald's and getting it "have it your way.

00:18:32.400 --> 00:18:38.520
" But what I am trying to tell you is that what I have seen is worse than the 1930s.

00:18:39.569 --> 00:18:55.733
I saw people rioting and pillaging the rich and the middle class, stealing whatever they wanted because there were tent cities everywhere and they didn't have enough money even for prescription medicines, and people were acting a fool just in little towns.

00:18:58.400 --> 00:19:01.173
You thought COVID was bad, when they were stealing toilet paper and acting the way they did.

00:19:14.268 --> 00:19:14.520
I saw a 1930s-style crash that was worse than anything you could ever imagine.

00:19:19.360 --> 00:19:20.320
And there was rioting, pillaging, and even farmers trying to pick people off at 50 yards, trying to protect their homestead.

00:19:20.320 --> 00:19:22.140
This is not what we want in America.

00:19:22.320 --> 00:19:32.368
And if we don't stand as the body of Christ with a backbone like a crowbar and pray for our nation and get us this window, it's all on us.

00:19:32.368 --> 00:19:38.600
Even Brother Hagin said, "If the church doesn't stand, what we see in the nation is because the church didn't stand.

00:19:38.600 --> 00:19:40.173
" Did I say that right?

00:19:40.173 --> 00:19:40.529
Yeah.

00:19:40.529 --> 00:19:51.120
Sometimes it comes out and I go, "Okay," because Brother Hagin always talked about that when there were frogs coming up—he had a vision, and he saw these frogs.

00:19:51.120 --> 00:19:58.984
It was during Nixon, whenever Nixon had Watergate, and it was all during that time frame.

00:19:58.984 --> 00:20:18.696
And Brother Hagin was interceding for America, and he said any kind of things that happen in our government is the church's fault if we don't take our authority and we don't pray that God would hold us accountable.

00:20:24.296 --> 00:20:24.600
And Brother Hagin went into all of it and had his prophetic word.

00:20:24.600 --> 00:20:33.794
One time I'll probably find it and Diana can read it to you.

00:20:33.794 --> 00:20:39.735
But I just want to tell you all, you've got to believe God for big.

00:20:39.735 --> 00:20:40.915
There's a reprieve.

00:20:40.915 --> 00:20:46.987
God is giving us the opportunity for a reprieve and for blessing on this nation.

00:20:46.987 --> 00:20:49.022
But the enemy doesn't want it to happen.

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:57.206
And we must contend and fight and say, "No, we will be walking in the blessing.

00:20:57.206 --> 00:21:08.671
We will have what God has for us and we will reap what we've sowed.

00:21:12.418 --> 00:21:12.636
" The goodness of God is on us.

00:21:15.267 --> 00:21:16.373
And I'm telling you, goodness and mercy will follow us.

00:21:17.111 --> 00:21:19.240
And that's what the Lord told me.

00:21:32.800 --> 00:21:41.133
He said, "You pray for those Supreme Court justices to make the decisions for the tariffs to balance the economy, to do the things, because right now there is no plan B.

00:21:49.622 --> 00:21:49.920
" And most people don't want to hear that.

00:21:49.920 --> 00:21:51.949
"Well, what happens if it doesn't happen?

00:21:51.949 --> 00:21:56.013
" Well, the "what if" is you better have a stockpile of food.

00:22:13.166 --> 00:22:13.972
That's what I would say.

00:22:13.972 --> 00:22:22.735
What if—in my opinion, and I'm entitled to my opinion.

00:22:22.735 --> 00:22:28.866
You know, people say, "You told me to buy food.

00:22:35.587 --> 00:22:35.840
" I ain't telling you to buy nothing.

00:22:35.840 --> 00:22:38.280
I ain't telling you to stock nothing.

00:22:52.271 --> 00:22:52.863
That's on you.

00:22:52.863 --> 00:22:59.251
If you feel you're supposed to do that, you do it.

00:22:59.251 --> 00:23:00.489
If not, don't.

00:23:00.489 --> 00:23:01.742
I don't care what you do.

00:23:09.750 --> 00:23:10.000
I'm not responsible for you; I'm responsible for my family.

00:23:10.000 --> 00:23:17.131
I'm here to tell you what I see and what I pray over.

00:23:19.947 --> 00:23:24.160
You do what you feel God has called you to do.

00:23:24.160 --> 00:23:35.280
My mom was telling me about some wheat and stuff that she's doing and making bread and all kinds of stuff.

00:23:35.280 --> 00:23:41.907
People have all kinds of ideas by the Holy Spirit because of what they're feeling in their insides.

00:23:44.270 --> 00:23:46.925
You just have to be following what the Holy Spirit tells you to do.

00:23:46.925 --> 00:23:53.730
If he tells you to buy wheat and make bread, then buy wheat and make bread.

00:23:53.730 --> 00:23:57.980
If he tells you to have a tower garden, have a tower garden.

00:23:57.980 --> 00:24:06.668
It's like when Mary spoke to the people at the marriage feast and she said, "Whatever he tells you to do, do it.

00:24:06.668 --> 00:24:10.560
" Everyone's circumstance is going to be different.

00:24:10.560 --> 00:24:12.126
It's not all cookie-cutter.

00:24:29.748 --> 00:24:35.100
If you live in New York—I can't even imagine living there—but if you do and God's called you to be there, it's going to be a lot different than what it is in Alabama, or in Texas out in the panhandle.

00:24:35.100 --> 00:24:51.840
It's a lot different in the panhandle of Texas than it is in New York.

00:25:00.900 --> 00:25:01.230
I can assure you, in Pampa or any of those towns out there, it's just an oil field town.

00:25:13.965 --> 00:25:14.308
You go through there and think, 'Wow, you see tumbleweeds.

00:25:14.308 --> 00:25:21.595
' But everybody tries to think about what it's going to be like in Miami.

00:25:32.380 --> 00:25:32.880
I have no idea.

00:25:33.340 --> 00:25:37.764
I went to Miami and couldn't wait to get out of there.

00:25:39.467 --> 00:25:45.760
I was looking at my rearview mirror; I went halfway, felt what was going on there, and said, 'Get out of here.

00:25:45.760 --> 00:25:50.095
' I turned around and went back up to West Palm Beach.

00:25:50.095 --> 00:25:54.364
Being real, I said, 'God, we're getting out of here quick.

00:25:54.364 --> 00:25:57.703
' Okay, let's go back and be serious.

00:25:57.703 --> 00:26:00.430
